{
  "stem": "24830.2",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The problem is, sometimes it takes so long, because the-- the underground will destroy the-- you know, the rail.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Everybody knew.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I didn't know-- my underground, I knew the people there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But the man in charge-- Henri Pohoryles is one, and Maurice Cachou, who finally was caught in Paris.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he was-- unfortunate-- well, he became so-- he was so smart, that he went to France, and he was in charge of all the false paper in in France.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Maurice Cachou That was the young-- I have his other name.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he was caught with a list, unfortunately.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was caught with a lot of my friends.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And because he have a list, they torture him so much that he die under torture.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They threw him in the-- [BACKROUND NOISE] I heard took the skin out.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "God knows what they did.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was horrible what they did.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He was all bloody.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I don't even want to describe it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "With the other-- my friend were caught, that they put-- you know, they put your head in the-- in the water-- in the bathtub, till you can not breathe.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And as soon as-- and then they bring you up.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And then they beat you.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And they torture you.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And for the women, it was even worse.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, half of the people who work with me never came back.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Like, for example, we meet-- well, everything was done on the bicycle.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, there was no-- there was no car anyway.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But so we'll meet in a certain [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] street, [FRENCH]-- [FRENCH] like, you know, Columbus Circle, or something like this.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we change place all the time, so-- and then we bicycle, and we talk.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We don't-- we don't stop too much.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
